* **Draft Splitting**: The authors of the proposed ciphertext inference tool draft will revise and split the document. The privacy analysis and FHE evaluation will be adapted to fit the PEARG charter, while the protocol integration details will be referred to the MCP Foundation.
* **Action Item (Chairs)**: **Sarah Dickinson** and **Shivan Sahib** will open a dedicated discussion on the PEARG mailing list to frame research questions regarding source privacy and assess how the proposed ECH mitigation concepts fit into the group's charter.

